# Player, UI & Audio Context

You are working on player, shared UI, or audio systems. Read these docs:

1. `docs/design/core-architecture.md` — shared patterns, project structure, event bus contracts
2. `docs/design/prototype-scope.md` — phase priorities and what belongs in v0.1 vs later
3. `docs/design/extensible-development-contracts.md` — UI runtime bridge and interaction workflow guardrails
4. Domain doc(s) affected by your change (for example reloading, world, inventory/economy)
5. `.agent/skills/unity-project-conventions/SKILL.md` — project conventions for scripts/assets

Do NOT load unrelated deep domain docs unless the change explicitly crosses that boundary.
